4941, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"One two three, viva l'Alg\\u00e9rie!\\\"\", \"from\": 2612, \"to\": 2644, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"fans celebrated in the stand.\", \"from\": 2645, \"to\": 2674, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 25-year-old Algerian boxer had just qualified for the quarter-finals of the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 2675, \"to\": 2770, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2691, \"end\": 2699, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9987179307605097, \"rank\": 0.001283715050886113, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The story might have ended there if Carini had not tearfully left the ring exclaiming, \\\"It is not fair!,\\\" providing a powerful echo to an insistent rumor born during the 2023 World Boxing Championships in New Delhi: that Khelif is not a woman.\", \"from\": 2771, \"to\": 3014, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2807, \"end\": 2813, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999999897218004, \"rank\": 1.027806201515796e-08, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}, {\"begin\": 2976, \"end\": 2985, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Delhi\", \"score\": 0.8442417036240122, \"rank\": 0.18449490910840077, \"text\": \"New Delhi\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Delhi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Delhi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the minutes that followed, social media amplification turned the match into one of the biggest controversies of the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 3016, \"to\": 3147, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Italian prime minister, Giorgia Meloni, spoke out on X against a \\\"fight that was not on an equal footing,\\\" outraged that athletes with \\\"masculine characteristics\\\" were allowed to take part in women's competitions.\", \"from\": 3148, \"to\": 3365, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3152, \"end\": 3159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.8378682763567111, \"rank\": 0.19350413517197848, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}, {\"begin\": 3176, \"end\": 3190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giorgia_Meloni\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Giorgia Meloni\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giorgia_Meloni\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giorgia_Meloni\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From entrepreneur Elon Musk and his 200 million-plus subscribers on X to novelist JK Rowling, the usual critics of the \\\"woke ideology\\\" raised their voices to denounce a fight rigged by \\\"transgender\\\" Khelif.\", \"from\": 3366, \"to\": 3572, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3384, \"end\": 3393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Elon Musk\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\"}, {\"begin\": 3448, \"end\": 3458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"JK Rowling\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On X, the author of the Harry Potter saga turned anti-trans activist even saw in the boxer's face \\\"the smirk of a male\\\" who was \\\"enjoying the distress of a woman he's just punched in the head.\\\"\", \"from\": 3574, \"to\": 3767, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3598, \"end\": 3610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Potter\", \"score\": 0.9999999991123332, \"rank\": 8.876309396514059e-10, \"text\": \"Harry Potter\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Potter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Potter\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif even became part of the American presidential campaign when Republican candidate Donald Trump wrote, in his trademark indignant capital letters, on his Truth Social network: \\\"I will keep men out of women's sports!\\\"\", \"from\": 3768, \"to\": 3989, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3799, \"end\": 3807, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.006421969324694e-13, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 3835, \"end\": 3845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Second_Spanish_Republic\", \"score\": 0.9999999645297073, \"rank\": 3.5468603531705643e-08, \"text\": \"Republican\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Second_Spanish_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Second_Spanish_Republic\"}, {\"begin\": 3856, \"end\": 3868, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999993669917, \"rank\": 6.327536482189007e-10, \"text\": \"Donald Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A gimmick he would use right up until the eve of his re-election, lashing out in a campaign clip broadcast on November 3 and showing a photo of Khelif, as the voice-over claimed that